        Song: It is the constructor in charge of storing the information of the songs to be able to add them, and it is audio inheritance.
        Parameters:
        nickname: - String => It is the nickname with which the owner of the song will be identified.
        name: - String => It is the name that the song will have.
        album: - String => It is the name of the album that will store the song.
        urlImage: - String => It is the image that will have the cover that will identify the song.
        timeRep: - int => It is the time in seconds that the playback of the song will have.
        price: - double => It is the sale price that the song will have to the public.
        genre: - int => It is the genre that the song to register will have.
